# Project Context

## Stack

- Node.js
- Git / GitHub for version control

## Conventions

- Commit messages follow Conventional Commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, chore:)
- Keep README updated as the project evolves
- .env files are never committed (see .gitignore)

## Purpose

This repo is the capstone project's setup phase — establishing a working AI-assisted development toolchain (IDE + AI assistant + git workflow) before building the main capstone project.
